Using QueryString for Notification:
Single Query String: ?keyname = value
multiple QueryString : ? keyname1 = value1 & keyname2 = value2 & keyname3 = value3 .......

Whenever you work with queryString there are multiple cache related problems like autofilling.

autocomplete = "off"
Tag level :<input type="text" name="name" autocomplete="off"/>



